channel.title: ProjectF2P - A F2P Remake In 2006
channel.description:
[center]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7lMBdR2wcFs
[b]Welcome to Project ProjectF2P[/b] Here at Project PF2P, we aim to replicate every single aspect of a Free-To-Play RuneScape world in 2006, while hosting a stable server, active community and maintaining security. We guarantee to have to most replicated and accurate F2P RSPS from the 2006 era of Runescape. We work with a very active and professional staff team across both the website and game. You'll notice our website is very easy to use and has a lot of relevant content. If you wish to register an account for free at our website, please just drop me a private message and I'll respond within 12 hours. We hope to have the server in a 3 day closed BETA for some of our trusted members in the beginning of February and have an 7 day open BETA for everybody towards the end of February
[B]The Team[/B] The current staff team are very professional bunch and are made to follow strict policies ensuring all of our staff members are the greatest you'll ever see. The team currently consist of [B]1[/B] Administrator/Lead Developer,[B]0[/B] Community Manager(s)[/COLOR] and [B]1[/B] Moderator(s).
[B]Please Note:[/B] I find it very hard to constantly update every single project thread on all the important RSPS resource websites, so instead of listing every single feature and how a skill works etc, simply visit the website, we provide a constant source of News & Updates on there.
[IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/x57a07.png[/img][/center]
